<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann III. von Hohenzollern, Burggraf von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Vermittlung im Streit um den Zehnt zu Schlaifhausen und Dobenreuth zwischen Christine von Wildenstein, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg, und dem burggräflichen Diener Georg Gottsmann, ihrem Bruder.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_152" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_152_r1l18"><expan>Burgr<ex>af</ex></expan> Johanſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_152_r1l19">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / vns hat fürgelegt / fraw Criſtein die <expan>wyldenſtein<ex>er</ex>ın</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l20"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> / vvie daʒ ſie Gorg Gocʒman <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> . Jr pruder an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l21">Jren cʒehenden cʒu Slaiffhawſen vnd on Tobernrewte Jrre vnd enge . / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l22">vnd die eingeſammet vnd hinweg gefurt hab . / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l23"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden mit <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchicken vnd beſtellen wollet durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l24"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> wılligen dinſt wıllen / daʒ er die <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> an <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l25">Jren <expan>cʒehend<ex>en</ex></expan> vngeenget laſʒe / vnd waʒ er der eingeſammet hab / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l26">er Ir daʒ widergebe / Als wir <expan>ew<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>e<ex>t</ex>c</expan> daʒ <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>e<ex>t</ex>c</expan> . vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l27">het dann 
<del rend="strikethrough">deſ </del> <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> icht cʒuſprechen . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l28">vt in forma / Antwurtt / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in vigilia Bartholomei <expan>ap<ex>oſto</ex>li</expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_152" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Burgr<ex>af</ex></expan> Johansen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt fraw Cristein, die
                                <expan>Wyldenstein<ex>er</ex>in</expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, wie daz sie Gorg Goczman,
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, ir pruder, an iren czehenden czu
                        Slaiffhawsen und on Tobernrewte irre und enge und die eingesammet und hinweg
                        gefurt hab. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden mit
                            <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> schicken und bestellen wollet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> willigen dinst willen, daz er die
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> an <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iren
                                <expan>czehend<ex>en</ex></expan> ungeenget lasze und, waz er der
                        eingesammet hab, daz er ir daz widergebe, als wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>e<ex>t</ex>c</expan>. Daz <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>e<ex>t</ex>c</expan>. Und het dann
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> czu <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> icht czu sprechen, ut in forma. Antwurtt.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in vigilia Bartholomei
                                <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
